{"tid":308892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[毒撚打J] 瞓床打機4日夜 失禁皮膚潰爛生褥瘡！","createTime":"2017-07-04T14:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T23:37:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebdac8f5cf1f1f66f8381c94091588e021c4843","tid":308892,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"浙江杭州一名22歲男子失業後躲在租住的單位內，日日夜夜對着電腦打機，連續4日未進食，更因為失禁無法自理，一直躺在滲滿尿液的床上不能動彈，致皮膚潰爛，還長褥瘡。直至友人近日致電給他發現有異，才及時將其救出送往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n當時，阿強獨自躺在床上，神志恍惚，面黃肌瘦，右下肢腫脹青紫，全身多處皮膚潰爛。據阿強說，已4天未進食。床上還可見有尿迹，一部開啟中的手提電腦。在場警員立即將阿強送往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170704/56907324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170704%2F56907324&d=T%2BvWPpznbk5CqmqUx5SEANr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c071e201\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170704%2F56907324&h=8dbc6f2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170704/56907324</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e066724ce4f40edd98d01b310f00390e647cec","tid":308892,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"失業後躲在租住的單位內，<span style=\"color: red;\">日日夜夜對着AV打J</span>，連續4日未進食，更因為失禁無法自理，一直躺在滲滿尿液的床上不能動彈，致皮膚潰爛，還長褥瘡。直至友人近日致電給他發現有異，才及時將其救出送往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n當時，阿強獨自躺在床上，神志恍惚，面黃肌瘦，右下肢腫脹青紫，全身多處皮膚潰爛。據阿強說，已4天未進食。床上還可見有尿迹，一部開啟中的手提電腦。在場警員立即將阿強送往醫院。"},{"pid":"2b9409a0b767cbc0b00e94d2f2a02ab553394632","tid":308892,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"@老貓再世_<br />\n<br />\nU<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\